dct_title_s: Misr, miqyas ar-rasm 1:25,000: al-Hammad, lawhat 98/630 = Egypt 1:25,000: El Hammad, sheet 98/630
dct_description_sm: Egypt. Maslahat al-Misahah al-Misriyah. Egypt. Egyptian Department of Surveys. Relief is shown by contour intervals. Heights shown by spot heights and bench marks. Includes indexes to adjoining sheets and village and district boundaries.
